---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 34
Tags:
  - Creation=Creation as Play or Sport
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=The Inner Pilgrimage
Commentary: From a Hindu Song
Glossary:
  Term: Vrindâvan
  Definition: A town associated with Krishna's childhood.
---
Go seek, O mind, go seek Vrindâvan in your heart,
Where with His loving devotees
Sri Krishna sports eternally.
